---
// FomoBanner.astro - Urgency / Scarcity strip
---

<div class="fomo-strip">
  <div class="container fomo-inner">
    <span class="fomo-pulse"></span>
    <p>⚡ <strong>PERINGATAN:</strong> Harga bisa naik kapan saja tanpa pemberitahuan. <span class="fomo-highlight">Amankan aksesmu SEKARANG</span> sebelum terlambat.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .fomo-strip {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #dc2626 0%, #b91c1c 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 14px 0;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    z-index: 100;
  }

  .fomo-strip::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.15), transparent);
    animation: shimmer 3s infinite;
    transform: translateX(-100%);
  }

  @keyframes shimmer {
    0% { transform: translateX(-100%); }
    100% { transform: translateX(100%); }
  }

  .fomo-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .fomo-pulse {
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    background: #fbbf24;
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: blink 1s infinite;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  @keyframes blink {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0.3; }
  }

  .fomo-strip p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .fomo-highlight {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .fomo-strip p { font-size: 0.85rem; }
  }
</style>
